  "reference_number": "RUS1125",
  "remarks": "\nAndrey Grigoryevich GURYEV is a former Deputy Chair of the Board of Directors at PJSC PhosAgro, a leading Russian chemical company. Through his directorship at PJSC PhosAgro, which he held between 2013 and 2022, GURYEV has been involved in obtaining a benefit or supporting the Government of Russia by working as a director or equivalent, of an entity carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, namely the Russian chemicals sector. \n",
